BSServer
========

Open implementation of a server for Brawl Stars v26
written in Go.


Overview
--------

This project provides a minimal Brawl Stars server implementation intended
for research, learning, and experimentation.
It implements basic networking and battle handling logic and is
designed to be simple, lightweight, and easy to modify.


